Package org.ndnx.ndn.io.content

Interface Summary
UpdateListener Interface that allows external listeners to register to be notified when a network object receives an update.
 

Class Summary
Collection A representation of a collection of NDN objects, represented as a list of Link s.
Collection.CollectionObject A NDNNetworkObject wrapper around Collection, used for easily saving and retrieving versioned Collections to NDN.
ConfigSlice  
ConfigSlice.Filter Config slice lists require a ConfigSliceOp written before the ContentName, although it does nothing.
ConfigSliceObject  
EncodableObject<E extends XMLEncodable> Subclass of NetworkObject that wraps classes implementing XMLEncodable, and uses XMLEncodable's encode() and decode() methods to read and write those objects to an OutputStream.
Header A Header is a set of metadata describing a particular NDN stream; basically it provides summary file-level information about that set of content.
Header.HeaderObject A NDNNetworkObject wrapper around Header, used for easily saving and retrieving versioned Headers to NDN.
KeyDirectory A key directory holds a key (secret or private), distributed to entities (represented by public keys), by a set of key blocks each of which wrapping that key under different target keys.
KeyValuePair  
KeyValuePair.KeyOrderComparator This can be used in a data structure to order KV pairs by their keys.
KeyValueSet  
KeyValueSet.KeyValueSetObject A NDNNetworkObject wrapper around KeyValueSet, used for easily saving and retrieving versioned KeyValueSets to NDN.
Link Represents a secure, authenticatable link from one part of the NDN namespace to another.
Link.LinkObject A NDNNetworkObject wrapper around Link, used for easily saving and retrieving versioned Links to NDN.
LinkAuthenticator A specifier for the information that can be used to authenticate the target of a Link.
LocalCopyListener A listener for a network object that requests a local repository to hold a copy of the object whenever it is updated or saved.
LocalCopyWrapper Wrapper for a generic network object that requests a local repository to hold a copy of the object whenever it is updated or saved.

NDNStringObject A NDNNetworkObject wrapper around Java Strings, which uses Java serialization to write those strings.
NetworkObject<E> A NetworkObject provides support for storing an object in a network based backing store.
PublicKeyObject A NDNNetworkObject subclass specialized for reading and writing PublicKeys.
SerializableObject<E extends Serializable> Subclass of NetworkObject that wraps classes implementing Serializable, and uses Java serialization to read and write those objects to an OutputStream.

WrappingKeyName A subtype of ContentName that encodes on the wire with a different label.
